</minor-heading>

<speech id="uk.org.publicwhip/wms/2008-03-12a.140.1" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/lord/100164" speakername="Lord Davies of Oldham" colon=":" colnum="140"  url="http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/ld200708/ldhansrd/text/80312-wms0001.htm#08031243000008">
	<p pid="a.140.1/1">My honourable friend the Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury (Angela Eagle) has made the following Written Ministerial Statement.</p>
	<p pid="a.140.1/2">The <I>Debt </I><I>and</I><I></I><I>Reserves Management Report 2008-09</I> is being published today. Copies have been deposited in the Library of the House.</p>
</speech>
